  "instructions": [
    "Preheat binchotan charcoal grill to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Season trout fillets with salt, black pepper, and grated ginger.",
    "Grill trout fillets for 4 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Cook pappardelle according to package instructions until al dente.",
    "In a blender or food processor, combine lemon juice, olive oil, garlic, and egg yolks. Blend until smooth.",
    "Strain pasta water through a fine-mesh sieve into a bowl, whisking in white wine vinegar.",
    "Add pasta water emulsion to blender or food processor with garlic-lemon mixture. Blend until smooth.",
    "Add chopped fresh dill to the emulsion and blend until combined.",
    "To assemble, place cooked pappardelle on a plate, top with grilled trout, and drizzle with pasta water emulsion.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
